Definition: a seizure of short duration characterized by momentary unconsciousness and local muscle spasms or twitching
Example: the girl was frightened by her first petit mal
Synonyms: epilepsia_minor, epileptic_seizure, a, seizure, of, short, duration, characterized, by, momentary, unconsciousness, and, local, muscle, spasms, or, twitching, the, girl, was, frightened, her, first, petit, mal
Category: noun.state
